99<>sage<>02/03/13 21:58 ID:RkXFZb3H<> <a href="../test/read.cgi/hp/1005046309/117" target="_blank">&gt;&gt;117</a> <br> リージョン内ならば、多分こんなで。 <br>  <br> (defun foo (from to) <br>   (interactive "*r") <br>   (save-excursion <br>     (save-restriction <br>       (narrow-to-region from to) <br>       (goto-char (point-min)) <br>       (replace-buffer "\\([^\n]\\)\t" "\\1\n\t" :regexp t) <br>       (goto-char (point-min)) <br>       (replace-buffer "\t\\([^\n]+\\)" "\t&lt;dd&gt;\\1&lt;/dd&gt;" :regexp t) <br>       (goto-char (point-min)) <br>       (replace-buffer "^\\([^\t\n]+\\)$" "&lt;dt&gt;\\1&lt;/dt&gt;" :regexp t)))) <>
