Name_Not_Found<>sage<>03/12/03 08:56 ID:???<> <a href="../test/read.cgi/hp/1005046309/650" target="_blank">&gt;&gt;650</a> <br> 簡単ですか？ <>
Name_Not_Found<>sage<>03/12/03 09:17 ID:???<> はい <>
Name_Not_Found<>sage<>03/12/03 10:25 ID:???<> ;; バッファから送るのリスト <br> (setf *buffer-send-to-list* <br>       (list <br>        '(" Internet Explorer" . "C:/Program Files/Internet Explorer/IEXPLORE.EXE") <br>        '(" Sleipnir" . "C:/Program Files/sleipnir/Sleipnir.exe") <br>        )) <br>  <br> ;; バッファから送る <br> (defun buffer-sendto-dialog () <br>   (interactive) <br>   (let ((file (get-buffer-file-name))) <br>     (when file <br>       (multiple-value-bind (result data) <br>   (dialog-box <br>    '(dialog 0 0 219 100 <br>      (:caption "送っちゃうよ") <br>      (:font 9 "Microsoft Sans Serif") <br>      (:control <br>       (:listbox list nil #x50b10111 7 7 150 82) <br>       (:button IDOK "送る" #x50010001 162 7 50 14) <br>       (:button IDCANCEL "送らない" #x50010000 162 24 50 14))) <br>    (list (cons 'list *buffer-send-to-list*)) <br>    nil) <br> (when result <br>   (let <br>       ((cmd (cddr (assoc 'list data)))) <br>     (if cmd <br> (call-process (map-slash-to-backslash (concat cmd " " file)) :wait nil) <br>       (message "なにもえらんでない。")))))))) <br> (define-key *global-keymap* '(#\c-F7) 'buffer-sendto-dialog) <br>  <>
Name_Not_Found<>sage<>03/12/03 10:26 ID:???<> ↑どっかで拾ったやつです。 <br>  <br>  <>
Name_Not_Found<><>03/12/03 15:20 ID:hACR5Pkw<> ;; C-F1で編集中のファイルを関連付け実行 <br> (defun execute () <br>   (interactive) <br>   (shell-execute (get-buffer-file-name))) <br> (global-set-key #\C-F1 'execute) <br>  <>
