Name_Not_Found<>sage<>05/02/10 23:29:43 ID:???<> <a href="../test/read.cgi/hp/1005046309/835" target="_blank">&gt;&gt;835</a> <br> あんまりテストしてないから注意して使って <br>  <br> (defun hoge () <br>   (interactive "*") <br>   (long-operation <br>     (let ((count 0)) <br>       (while (scan-buffer "[A-Z/---]" :regexp t) <br>         (if (eq (parse-point-syntax) ':tag) <br>             (progn (downcase-region (progn (skip-syntax-spec-backward "w_") (point)) <br>                                     (progn (skip-syntax-spec-forward "w_") (point))) <br>             (incf count)) <br>         (scan-buffer "[^A-Z/---]" :regexp t))) <br>       (message " ~D個変換しましたゼ" count)))) <>
